## 1. Purpose

This policy establishes the requirements for assessing, onboarding, and continuously monitoring third-party AI tool vendors. It ensures {{ business_name }} meets its obligations under the Privacy Act 1988 (APP 8 — Cross-Border Disclosure), OAIC AI Guidance (October 2024), and the POLA Act 2024 when engaging external AI service providers.

## 2. Scope

This policy applies to all AI tools and services provided by third-party vendors that:

- Process, store, or have access to {{ business_name }} data
- Are used by any employee, contractor, or agent of {{ business_name }}
- Generate outputs used in business operations or customer-facing activities

